    {
      "title": "Funktionsbegriff & Wertetabelle",
      "html": "<h3 style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;\">Was ist eine Funktion?</h3>\n<div style=\"background:#eff6ff;border:1.5px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin:10px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin:0;\">Eine <strong>Funktion</strong> ordnet jedem x-Wert <em>genau einen</em> y-Wert zu. Die Vorschrift heißt <strong>Funktionsgleichung</strong>.</p></div>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin:8px 0;\">f(x) = mx + b</div><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;text-align:center;margin-top:4px;\">Alle linearen Funktionen haben diese Form.</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:10px 0 6px 0;\"><strong>Wertetabelle</strong> für f(x) = 2x + 1:</p>\n<table style=\"width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:12px;\">\n  <tr style=\"background:#1C1B1F;color:#fff;\"><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;font-weight:600;\">x</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">−2</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">−1</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">0</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">1</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">2</td></tr>\n  <tr><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;font-weight:600;background:#f5f5f5;\">f(x)</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">−3</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">−1</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;font-weight:700;color:#2563eb;\">1</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">3</td><td style=\"padding:6px 10px;\">5</td></tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;\">💡 <strong>b</strong> ist der y-Wert bei x = 0 — einfach direkt aus der Tabelle ablesen!</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "Steigung & Steigungsdreieck",
      "html": "<h3 style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;\">Steigung m berechnen</h3>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin:8px 0;\">m = Δy / Δx = Höhenunterschied / Streckenunterschied</div>\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;margin:10px 0 6px 0;\">Zeichne ein <strong>Steigungsdreieck</strong> an die Gerade:</p>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n  <div><svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 170\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:220px;display:block;\"><defs><marker id=\"ah\" markerWidth=\"8\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L8,3 z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"38\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"38\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"56\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"56\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"74\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"74\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"92\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"92\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"128\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"128\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"146\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"146\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"164\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"164\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"182\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"182\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"38\" y1=\"157\" x2=\"182\" y2=\"157\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"38\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"182\" y2=\"139\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"38\" y1=\"121\" x2=\"182\" y2=\"121\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"38\" y1=\"103\" x2=\"182\" y2=\"103\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"38\" y1=\"85\" x2=\"182\" y2=\"85\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"38\" y1=\"67\" x2=\"182\" y2=\"67\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"38\" y1=\"49\" x2=\"182\" y2=\"49\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"38\" y1=\"31\" x2=\"182\" y2=\"31\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"38\" y1=\"13\" x2=\"182\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"32.60000000000001\" y1=\"85\" x2=\"191.0\" y2=\"85\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#ah)\"/><line x1=\"110\" y1=\"162.39999999999998\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"4.0\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#ah)\"/><text x=\"38\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-4</text><text x=\"56\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-3</text><text x=\"74\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-2</text><text x=\"92\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-1</text><text x=\"128\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">1</text><text x=\"146\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">2</text><text x=\"164\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">3</text><text x=\"182\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">4</text><text x=\"105\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-4</text><text x=\"105\" y=\"142\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-3</text><text x=\"105\" y=\"124\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-2</text><text x=\"105\" y=\"106\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-1</text><text x=\"105\" y=\"70\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">1</text><text x=\"105\" y=\"52\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">2</text><text x=\"105\" y=\"34\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">3</text><text x=\"105\" y=\"16\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">4</text><text x=\"196.0\" y=\"89\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#666\">x</text><text x=\"114\" y=\"1.0\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#666\">y</text><line x1=\"38.0\" y1=\"193.0\" x2=\"182.0\" y2=\"-23.0\" stroke=\"#2563eb\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><line x1=\"92.0\" y1=\"112.0\" x2=\"128.0\" y2=\"112.0\" stroke=\"#15803d\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,2\"/><line x1=\"128.0\" y1=\"112.0\" x2=\"128.0\" y2=\"58.0\" stroke=\"#dc2626\" stroke-width=\"1.8\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,2\"/><text x=\"110.0\" y=\"126.0\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#15803d\" font-weight=\"bold\">Δx = 2</text><text x=\"136.0\" y=\"85.0\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#dc2626\" font-weight=\"bold\">Δy = 3</text><circle cx=\"92.0\" cy=\"112.0\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#2563eb\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><circle cx=\"128.0\" cy=\"58.0\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#2563eb\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/></svg></div>\n  <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:150px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:#eff6ff;border:1.5px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin:10px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;\">➜ Gehe <span style=\"color:#15803d;font-weight:700;\">Δx = 2</span> Schritte nach rechts<br>➜ Gehe <span style=\"color:#dc2626;font-weight:700;\">Δy = 3</span> Schritte nach oben<br>➜ m = 3/2 = <strong>1,5</strong></p></div>\n    <p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;margin-top:8px;\">⚠️ Geht die Gerade <strong>bergab</strong>, ist Δy negativ → m &lt; 0</p>\n  </div>\n</div>"
    },
    {
      "title": "Geradengleichung f(x) = mx + b",
      "html": "<h3 style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;\">Die Geradengleichung f(x) = mx + b</h3>\n<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:12px;margin-bottom:12px;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#eff6ff;border:1.5px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin:10px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;\"><strong>m</strong> = Steigung<br>Gibt an, wie steil die Gerade ist.<br>m &gt; 0 → steigt &nbsp;|&nbsp; m &lt; 0 → fällt<br>m = 0 → waagerecht</p></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#fffbeb;border:1.5px solid #fde68a;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin:10px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.8;margin:0;\"><strong>b</strong> = y-Achsenabschnitt<br>Wo schneidet die Gerade die y-Achse?<br>→ Einfach bei x = 0 ablesen:<br>f(0) = m·0 + b = <strong>b</strong></p></div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap;\">\n  <div><svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 170\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:220px;display:block;\"><defs><marker id=\"ah\" markerWidth=\"8\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L8,3 z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"26\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"26\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"44\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"44\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"62\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"62\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"80\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"80\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"98\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"98\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"116\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"116\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"134\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"134\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"152\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"152\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"170\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"26\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"139\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"26\" y1=\"121\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"121\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"26\" y1=\"103\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"103\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"26\" y1=\"85\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"85\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"26\" y1=\"67\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"67\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"26\" y1=\"49\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"49\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"26\" y1=\"31\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"31\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"26\" y1=\"13\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"26\" y1=\"-5\" x2=\"170\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"20.6\" y1=\"85\" x2=\"179.0\" y2=\"85\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#ah)\"/><line x1=\"80\" y1=\"144.4\" x2=\"80\" y2=\"-14.0\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#ah)\"/><text x=\"26\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-3</text><text x=\"44\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-2</text><text x=\"62\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-1</text><text x=\"98\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">1</text><text x=\"116\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">2</text><text x=\"134\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">3</text><text x=\"152\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">4</text><text x=\"170\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">5</text><text x=\"75\" y=\"142\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-3</text><text x=\"75\" y=\"124\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-2</text><text x=\"75\" y=\"106\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-1</text><text x=\"75\" y=\"70\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">1</text><text x=\"75\" y=\"52\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">2</text><text x=\"75\" y=\"34\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">3</text><text x=\"75\" y=\"16\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">4</text><text x=\"75\" y=\"-2\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">5</text><text x=\"184.0\" y=\"89\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#666\">x</text><text x=\"84\" y=\"-17.0\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#666\">y</text><line x1=\"26.0\" y1=\"103.0\" x2=\"170.0\" y2=\"-41.0\" stroke=\"#2563eb\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"80.0\" cy=\"49.0\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#d97706\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><text x=\"86.0\" y=\"44.0\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#d97706\" font-weight=\"bold\">b=2</text><line x1=\"26.0\" y1=\"85.0\" x2=\"170.0\" y2=\"85.0\" stroke=\"none\"/><text x=\"134.0\" y=\"-5.0\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#2563eb\" font-weight=\"bold\">f(x)=x+2</text><line x1=\"98.0\" y1=\"31.0\" x2=\"116.0\" y2=\"31.0\" stroke=\"#15803d\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"4,2\"/><line x1=\"116.0\" y1=\"31.0\" x2=\"116.0\" y2=\"13.0\" stroke=\"#dc2626\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-dasharray=\"4,2\"/><text x=\"107.0\" y=\"43.0\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#15803d\">+1</text><text x=\"123.0\" y=\"22.0\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#dc2626\">+1</text></svg></div>\n  <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:150px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:#eff6ff;border:1.5px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin:10px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.9;margin:0;\">Beispiel: <strong>f(x) = x + 2</strong><br>m = <span style=\"color:#15803d;font-weight:700;\">1</span> (pro Schritt rechts, 1 hoch)<br>b = <span style=\"color:#d97706;font-weight:700;\">2</span> (Schnittpunkt mit y-Achse)</p></div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
    },
    {
      "title": "Gleichung aus zwei Punkten",
      "html": "<h3 style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;\">Gleichung aus zwei Punkten</h3>\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;\">Gegeben: P₁(x₁|y₁) und P₂(x₂|y₂). Gesucht: f(x) = mx + b</p>\n<div style=\"background:#eff6ff;border:1.5px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin:10px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:6px;\">Schritt 1: Steigung berechnen</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin:8px 0;\">m = (y₂ − y₁) / (x₂ − x₁)</div></div>\n<div style=\"background:#fffbeb;border:1.5px solid #fde68a;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin:10px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:6px;\">Schritt 2: b bestimmen</p>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;margin:0;\">Einen Punkt (z.B. P₁) in <strong>y = mx + b</strong> einsetzen:<br>\ny₁ = m · x₁ + b &nbsp;→&nbsp; <strong>b = y₁ − m · x₁</strong></p></div>\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin:12px 0 6px 0;\">Beispiel: P₁(1|3) und P₂(3|7)</p>\n<div style=\"background:#f8f8f8;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;font-size:13px;font-family:monospace;line-height:2;\">\n  m = (7−3)/(3−1) = 4/2 = <strong>2</strong><br>\n  b = 3 − 2·1 = <strong>1</strong><br>\n  → f(x) = <strong>2x + 1</strong>\n</div>"
    },
    {
      "title": "Nullstellen bestimmen",
      "html": "<h3 style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;\">Nullstellen bestimmen</h3>\n<div style=\"background:#eff6ff;border:1.5px solid #bfdbfe;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin:10px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin:0;\">Die <strong>Nullstelle x₀</strong> ist der x-Wert, bei dem die Gerade die <strong>x-Achse schneidet</strong>, also f(x) = 0.</p></div>\n<div style=\"display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:10px 0;\">\n  <div><svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 170\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:220px;display:block;\"><defs><marker id=\"ah\" markerWidth=\"8\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\"><path d=\"M0,0 L0,6 L8,3 z\" fill=\"#555\"/></marker></defs><line x1=\"28\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"28\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"46\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"46\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"64\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"64\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"82\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"82\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"100\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"100\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"118\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"118\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"136\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"136\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"154\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"154\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"172\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"172\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"28\" y1=\"139\" x2=\"172\" y2=\"139\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"28\" y1=\"121\" x2=\"172\" y2=\"121\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"28\" y1=\"103\" x2=\"172\" y2=\"103\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"28\" y1=\"85\" x2=\"172\" y2=\"85\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"28\" y1=\"67\" x2=\"172\" y2=\"67\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"28\" y1=\"49\" x2=\"172\" y2=\"49\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"28\" y1=\"31\" x2=\"172\" y2=\"31\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"28\" y1=\"13\" x2=\"172\" y2=\"13\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"28\" y1=\"-5\" x2=\"172\" y2=\"-5\" stroke=\"#ebebeb\" stroke-width=\"0.8\"/><line x1=\"22.60000000000001\" y1=\"85\" x2=\"181.0\" y2=\"85\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#ah)\"/><line x1=\"100\" y1=\"144.4\" x2=\"100\" y2=\"-14.0\" stroke=\"#555\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" marker-end=\"url(#ah)\"/><text x=\"28\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-4</text><text x=\"46\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-3</text><text x=\"64\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-2</text><text x=\"82\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-1</text><text x=\"118\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">1</text><text x=\"136\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">2</text><text x=\"154\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">3</text><text x=\"172\" y=\"97\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">4</text><text x=\"95\" y=\"142\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-3</text><text x=\"95\" y=\"124\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-2</text><text x=\"95\" y=\"106\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">-1</text><text x=\"95\" y=\"70\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">1</text><text x=\"95\" y=\"52\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">2</text><text x=\"95\" y=\"34\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">3</text><text x=\"95\" y=\"16\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">4</text><text x=\"95\" y=\"-2\" text-anchor=\"end\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#aaa\">5</text><text x=\"186.0\" y=\"89\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#666\">x</text><text x=\"104\" y=\"-17.0\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#666\">y</text><line x1=\"28.0\" y1=\"247.0\" x2=\"172.0\" y2=\"31.0\" stroke=\"#2563eb\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><circle cx=\"136.0\" cy=\"85.0\" r=\"4\" fill=\"#dc2626\" stroke=\"white\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><text x=\"142.0\" y=\"80.0\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#dc2626\" font-weight=\"bold\">x₀=2</text><circle cx=\"136.0\" cy=\"85.0\" r=\"6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#dc2626\" stroke-width=\"2\"/></svg></div>\n  <div style=\"flex:1;min-width:160px;\">\n    <div style=\"background:#f8f8f8;border:1.5px solid #e5e5e5;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin:10px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:6px;\">Rechnerisch:</p>\n<div style=\"font-family:monospace;font-size:13px;line-height:2;\">f(x) = 1,5x − 3 = 0<br>1,5x = 3<br>x₀ = 3 ÷ 1,5 = <strong>2</strong></div></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#555;\">💡 <strong>Merke:</strong> f(x) = 0 setzen, nach x auflösen → das ist die Nullstelle.</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "Sachaufgaben",
      "html": "<h3 style=\"font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;\">Sachaufgaben lösen</h3>\n<div style=\"background:#f5f3ff;border:1.5px solid #ddd6fe;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin:10px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin:0;\">Viele Alltagssituationen lassen sich durch lineare Funktionen beschreiben, wenn sich etwas <strong>gleichmäßig verändert</strong>.</p></div>\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:600;margin:12px 0 6px 0;\">Taxi-Beispiel: 2,50 € Grundpreis + 1,80 € pro km</p>\n<div style=\"background:#f8f8f8;border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;font-size:13px;line-height:2;\">\n  <strong>m</strong> = 1,80 (Änderungsrate: €/km)<br>\n  <strong>b</strong> = 2,50 (Startwert bei x=0)<br>\n  → <strong>f(x) = 1,80x + 2,50</strong>\n</div>\n<div style=\"background:#fffbeb;border:1.5px solid #fde68a;border-radius:10px;padding:14px 18px;margin:10px 0;\"><p style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;\">Vorgehen bei Sachaufgaben:</p>\n<ol style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:2;padding-left:18px;margin:0;\">\n  <li>Was ist x? (z.B. Kilometer, Zeit, Menge)</li>\n  <li>Was ist f(x)? (z.B. Preis, Entfernung)</li>\n  <li>Steigung m = Änderungsrate (pro Einheit)</li>\n  <li>b = Startwert (bei x = 0)</li>\n</ol></div>"
    }
  ]
}